    "ul": [
      "Microsoft® Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) 3.5 Microsoft Visual Studio® 2008",
      "For more information see “Selecting a Credential Type” at http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms733836.aspx"
